      <fr:mainmatter>
        <fr:tree toc="true" numbered="false" show-heading="true" show-metadata="true" expanded="false" root="false" xmlns:fr="http://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-005P.xml">
          <fr:frontmatter>
            <fr:anchor>282</fr:anchor>
            <fr:addr type="user">feats</fr:addr>
            <fr:route>feats.xml</fr:route>
            <fr:title text="Feats">Feats</fr:title>
            <fr:authors />
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <fr:p>Smite - righteous fury. Use before rolling a melee Attack: attack gains either +d12 or Blast. Pass a <fr:link type="local" href="virtues.xml" addr="virtues" title="Virtues"><fr:strong>VIG</fr:strong></fr:link> <fr:link type="local" href="saves.xml" addr="saves" title="Saves">Save</fr:link> or become <fr:link type="local" href="fatigue.xml" addr="fatigue" title="Fatigue">Fatigued</fr:link>.</fr:p>
            <fr:p>Focus - exploit an opening. Use after rolling an Attack: perform a gambit without using a die. Pass a <fr:strong>CLA</fr:strong> Save or become Fatigued.</fr:p>
            <fr:p>Deny - rebuff an attack. Use after an Attack roll against you or an ally within arm's reach, discard one Attack die from the roll. Pass a <fr:strong>SPI</fr:strong> Save or become Fatigued.</fr:p>
          </fr:mainmatter>
          <fr:backmatter />
        </fr:tree>
      </fr:mainmatter>
      <fr:backmatter />
    </fr:tree>
  </fr:backmatter>
</fr:tree>
